{"tid":482148,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有人以偽造基站干擾電話訊號，令用家被逼連入2G偽造基站以盜取資料","createTime":"2017-11-28T01:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T04:36:57.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"88f4d8caa50f7824cce69df7ba57855453008ef3","tid":482148,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:48:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1957154/偽基站強制連接手機防不勝防？方保僑：關掉%202G%20網絡\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1957154%2F%E5%81%BD%E5%9F%BA%E7%AB%99%E5%BC%B7%E5%88%B6%E9%80%A3%E6%8E%A5%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%98%B2%E4%B8%8D%E5%8B%9D%E9%98%B2%EF%BC%9F%E6%96%B9%E4%BF%9D%E5%83%91%EF%BC%9A%E9%97%9C%E6%8E%89%25202G%2520%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1&d=qd1qbqGz5wfWBr0zsx1ultZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=746ecc47\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1957154/偽基站強制連接手機防不勝防？方保僑：關掉%202G%20網絡</a><br />\n<br />\n通訊事務管理局辦公室（通訊辦）於上周四在上水的「目標處所」成功掃蕩一個偽冒基站，搜獲三部無線電設備，並拘捕一人到警署作進一步調查。偽冒基站是甚麼？對市民有甚麼影響？如何提防？<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=qd1qbqGz5wfWBr0zsx1ultZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=9070aae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 訪問了香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑（Francis）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  = <a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=qd1qbqGz5wfWBr0zsx1ultZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=9070aae7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  = 方保僑<br />\n<br />\n偽冒基站是如何操作？<br />\n<br />\n偽冒基站普遍使用 2G 流動電訊網絡進行。偽冒基站首先會發出干擾訊號，干擾一定範圍內的包括 4G 及 3G 基站訊號，令這個範圍的手機號碼接收不到正常流動網絡，這些手機號碼遂被強制吸入到 2G 偽冒基站，偽冒基站向被吸入的手機號碼發送大量 SMS 短訊，包括廣告宣傳、外圍賭博、甚至是詐騙等惡意行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n偽冒基站與手機連結的時間很短，當市民手機回復連接到正常流動網絡，然後打開 SMS 按下連結，可能進入了釣魚網站；或開啟不明檔案中了木馬程式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n在香港，參與外圍賭博是犯法的。由於偽冒基站網絡不易被追查，或因此被用作收受外圍賭博投注用途。<br />\n<br />\n還有，高階的偽冒基站更可用作截聽行為。"},{"pid":"c0074c032c4625cf1492ca7b396fd57119afc7a2","tid":482148,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12326781ff2d5b8acbb76d1cbc25a67b71b2247","tid":482148,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1957154/20171127_basestation_02s_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1957154%2F20171127_basestation_02s_600.jpg&h=e5de4c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">偽冒基站可流動</span></span><br />\n<br />\n通訊辦在上水打擊偽冒基站，反映偽冒基站有地區性？靠近北區危危乎？<br />\n<br />\n不，偽冒基站沒有地區性，可以是流動的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。現在的偽冒基站發射器較細小，不像從前大大件，只要加部筆電操控，放在車內就可變成偽冒流動基站，駕駛到市區，就會把該範圍的手機號碼吸進去強制接收 SMS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因此全港市民都有機會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"04e99cfce2291291bc292485df448ccb679a7812","tid":482148,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:51:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">關掉 2G 網絡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n市民如何提防偽冒基站？<br />\n<br />\n關掉 2G 網絡，避免被吸進偽冒基站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ；然而未必所有手機都具有此項功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。此外，市民在任何時候收到 SMS 短訊，都要提高警覺，不要胡亂按下超連結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、不要打開陌生檔案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ；即使發送者是相識的名字，例如某某快餐店或咖啡店，都要小心，可能也是偽冒的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1957154/20171127_basestation_03_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1957154%2F20171127_basestation_03_600.png&h=47eec5a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"488939afdcb96d61019b8b0f88d9fc4ec262b072","tid":482148,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:53:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">建基站必須領牌</span></span><br />\n<br />\n網店似有發售基站，也有關於自建基站的教學。所謂「偽冒基站」，是給不誠實使用基站的冠名而已？<br />\n<br />\n在香港，必須領有電訊牌照，才可以建立基站進行廣播，否則即屬違法。因此自建基站「冇乜合法用途」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，早前有朋友表示，民航客機也會在飛機上自建迷你基站，於飛航途中，讓乘客藉基站連接漫遊服務。<br />\n<br />\n編按：根據香港法例，任何人如沒有適當牌照管有或使用任何作無線電通訊之用的器具；或設置或維持任何電訊設施，即屬違法。一經定罪，最高可判處罰款 10 萬元及監禁 5 年。"},{"pid":"7887a4b5af533696c408485fa78f9029c22d98de","tid":482148,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:56:34.000Z","msg":"以為大陸先有"},{"pid":"baa47361a3b968bc20c3f4f73253e9f804536056","tid":482148,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:58:34.000Z","msg":"IT狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3e687d9160fc132da3caa675bf45595e249916","tid":482148,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T02:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IT狗<img s